  - Ward secretary se public budget aur responsibility handover lein
  - Shanti ke saath citizen-audit baseline publish karein
  - Water line ka pressure test aur measured payment verify karein
  - Free paperwork help desk aur receipt system shuru karein
  - Resident verification ke saath streetlight repair close karein
  - Community clinic ka medicine stock aur batch register audit karein
  - Non-partisan evening learning room aur attendance system shuru karein
  - Open e-tender ya unaudited verbal shortcut mein decision lein
  - Samrat ke saath non-partisan monsoon emergency route coordinate karein
  - Work-wise payment aur remaining budget public dashboard par publish karein
  - Independent moderator ke saath open jan-sunwai complete karein
  - Citizen audit panel par computed 100-day review dekhein
